snippet.title: Alien Creeps TD Game Trailer HD
snippet.description:
The aliens are here... and they didn't come in peace.  Can you save the Earth?

Alien Creeps TD is an explosive new tower defense game from Outplay Entertainment, out now on iPhone, iPad and iPod Touch! 

Alien Creeps TD is the tower defense game that has it all: frenzied, epic battles!  Hordes of devious enemies!  Dazzling graphics and animations!  Lighting bolts!  Helicopters!  

Blast those creeps with more than 50 powerful towers!  Mow them down with sturdy infantry units and courageous heroes!  Zap them with the supercharged Tesla Tower!  

Find out more: 
www.facebook.com/pages/AlienCreepsTD
https://twitter.com/AlienCreepsTD
